N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 5102.10 - Processing

State Regulations

The commission will process only complete applications. The commission will notify the video lottery gaming agent's human resource
department when an application has been accepted as complete. The processing of
any application shall not constitute the commission's concurrence that the
requirements of the act and these regulations have been
satisfied. Notes
